#

Coconut Curry Chicken with Rice

40 min
$12
450 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Coconut

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeDairy-Free

Cuisine:

Thai

Course:

Main Dish

Tags:

EasyQuickComfort Food

Description

A creamy and flavorful coconut curry chicken served over fluffy rice, perfect for a quick weeknight dinner.

Ingredients

  • chicken breast: 1 pound
  • coconut milk: 1 can (13.5 oz)
  • curry powder: 2 tablespoons
  • garlic: 3 cloves
  • onion: 1 medium
  • bell pepper: 1 medium
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • salt: to taste
  • rice: 1 cup
  • water: 2 cups
  • fresh cilantro: for garnish (optional)
